BTPLS - Bluetooth Proximity Screen Locker - Lock screen taking into consideration proximity of Bluetooth device.

Debian package files can be obtained here:
 - version 1:
        DEB - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Km7IrRAcKPLsy2Os8heQ6ekQP0eF-SvU
        MD5 - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1q4vuP45xlUfbBonNCvI9ZlcPCN55Rf7U

